NAME
    App::ArithmeticsUtils - Utilities related to arithmetics

VERSION
    This document describes version 0.001 of App::ArithmeticsUtils (from
    Perl distribution App-ArithmeticsUtils), released on 2026-02-26.

DESCRIPTION
    This distribution provides the following command-line utilities related
    to arithmetics:

    *   calc-divide-remainder

FUNCTIONS
  calc_divide_remainder
    Usage:

     calc_divide_remainder(%args) -> any

    A simple shortcut to calculate division (a / b) and remainder in one
    step.

    Examples:

    *   Example #1:

         calc_divide_remainder(a => 140, b => 6); # -> [23, 2]

    Keywords: modulo

    This function is not exported.

    Arguments ('*' denotes required arguments):

    *   a* => *float*

        (No description)

    *   b* => *float*

        (No description)

    Return value: (any)

